Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:04.79,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷你战国basara贰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.91,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收获！！月夜的片仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:17.39,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有趁着夜色而逃跑的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:36.70,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟会露出这般温柔的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.63,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊达家的头号大军师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:44.31,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之右目 这就是你真正的姿态吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:48.08,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这毫无遮掩的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:49.81,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战场上让众人看看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:05.88,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以政宗为首的伊达军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.40,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定会失去战意吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.83,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙对人还真是铁面无私啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.45,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你评价很高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.83,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才特地赶到这片田里的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:30.83,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:33.56,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安土城就不会被攻下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.28,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不这么觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:42.92,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:44.12,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:50.05,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何沉默不语…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:51.78,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为何一言不发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:56.38,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.49,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以缄口不语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.25,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让我变得急躁 而施下的计略吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:14.10,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说 这可真是个没有技术含量的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:19.73,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:22.94,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你 应该没有这份从容才是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:28.77,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手里可有伊达军的人质哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.73,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做笔交易吧 片仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:40.82,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你成为我丰臣军的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.64,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好斟酌一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:49.38,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据你的回答…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.10,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.40,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.68,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你原意？成为丰臣的军一员？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.08,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.32,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很不容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:06.09,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论刮风下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.73,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都一直自己保护着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:10.16,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.57,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我把你料理成为一顿美餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.81,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.50,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是半吊子的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.55,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你做成日本第一的味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.70,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.43,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在对葱说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.66,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹中半兵卫！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.65,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这厮 究竟是何时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.41,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫不是 你想对我家葱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.04,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片仓君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.12,Takenaka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对区区一根葱太执着了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.77,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有漏洞！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.37,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不要惹我哦
